# No barrel index files

- Do not add `index.ts` files that only re-export from sibling modules.
- Import directly from the concrete file (e.g. `@/lib/ai/tools/show-projects`).
- Tool registries and aggregators belong in a named file (e.g. `portfolio-tools.ts`), not `index.ts`.
